Source: liblely-libc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: J. S. Seldenthuis <jseldenthuis@lely.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), autotools-dev, cdbs, doxygen
Standards-Version: 3.9.7
Section: libs
Homepage: http://www.lely.com

Package: liblely-libc1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Description: C11 and POSIX compatibility library
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: liblely-libc1-dbg
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         liblely-libc1 (= ${binary:Version})
Multi-Arch: same
Description: C11 and POSIX compatibility library debugging symbols
 This package contains the debugging symbols.

Package: liblely-libc-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         liblely-libc1 (= ${binary:Version})
Suggests: liblely-libc-doc
Multi-Arch: same
Description: C11 and POSIX compatibility library development files
 This package contains the development files, static library and header files.

Package: liblely-libc-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: C11 and POSIX compatibility library documentation
 This package contains doxygen generated documentation.
